                            <p>Elite K9 is owned and run by Hanna Myers. A Tacoma based trainer who has been training for the past 16 years. Elite K9 offers everything from basic obedience to, agility, sports work and  specialized service dog task training and  public access training. Hanna Myers has been working with and training service dogs for over 16 years. Each client is given one on one personalized training. No group sessions. Our training methods use positive reinforcement and cue and correction training. We do not employ choke chains, pinch collars, E-collars or any dominant or fear tactic training. </p>
